  "original_title": "\u0db0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd3 \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dhanish Ali remanded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage ordered today (27) to remand Dhanish Ali, who was arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department in relation to a warrant issued by the Fort Court while he was on a flight preparing to go abroad.",
        "31-year-old Dhanish Ali, a resident of Kurunegala Webada area, was remanded.",
        "The Magistrate also ordered the prison to present the suspect under cover to the Colombo Chief Magistrate's Court on the 1st for an identification parade in a case related to a complaint filed by the Kurunduwatta Police regarding the alleged entry into the television corporation by force."
      ],
